    <item>
      <title>阿根廷顶级首席执行官在 Patagonia Retreat 盛赞 Milei</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/top-argentina-ceos-to-heap-praise-on-javier-milei-at-patagonia-retreat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于三位数的通货膨胀抑制了消费者支出，爱德华多·埃尔斯斯坦 (Eduardo Elsztain) 正准备迎接他的购物中心销售受到影响。然而哈维尔·米雷就任总统四个月后，这位房地产大亨比以往任何时候都更加看好阿根廷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/top-argentina-ceos-to-heap-praise-on-javier-milei-at-patagonia-retreat</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织称中美债务给全球公共财政带来风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/imf-says-us-china-debt-pose-risks-for-global-public-finances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织(IMF)官员表示，世界两大经济竞争对手中国和美国将在未来五年内推动全球公共债务的增长，而美国的支出通过维持高利率给许多其他国家带来麻烦。在一份报告中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/imf-says-us-china-debt-pose-risks-for-global-public-finances</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>渣打银行表示，斯里兰卡准备在五月中旬之前达成债券持有人协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/sri-lanka-poised-for-bondholder-deal-by-mid-may-stanchart-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行策略师表示，斯里兰卡可能会在 5 月中旬之前与投资者达成协议，重组其 120 亿美元的违约全球债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/sri-lanka-poised-for-bondholder-deal-by-mid-may-stanchart-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 12:58:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔的美国利率警告令世界其他地区头疼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/powell-s-us-rates-warning-means-headaches-for-rest-of-the-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔(Jerome Powell)正在让世界各地同行的日子变得更加艰难，因为美国利率长期走高的前景减少了其他地方宽松政策的空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/powell-s-us-rates-warning-means-headaches-for-rest-of-the-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 12:56:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰阿斯塔塔公司计划在欧盟以外的地区增加食糖销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/ukraine-s-astarta-targets-more-sugar-sales-outside-eu-amid-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着欧盟收紧对乌克兰的进口规定，乌克兰食糖生产商阿斯塔塔控股公司计划增加对欧盟以外的出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/ukraine-s-astarta-targets-more-sugar-sales-outside-eu-amid-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 12:55:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米其林挑战欧盟寻找轮胎卡特尔证据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/michelin-challenges-eu-s-hunt-for-evidence-of-tire-cartel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着监管机构席卷整个轮胎行业，寻找涉嫌垄断价格卡特尔的证据，米其林正在挑战欧盟对其设施进行反垄断搜查的合法性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/michelin-challenges-eu-s-hunt-for-evidence-of-tire-cartel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:03:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金价格保持在接近纪录水平，交易者不考虑以后降息的可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/gold-xauusd-holds-near-record-as-traders-overlook-delayed-cuts-scenario</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管投资者权衡美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的信息转变，金价仍稳定在历史高位附近，鲍威尔表示，美联储维持利率不变的时间可能会比原计划更长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/gold-xauusd-holds-near-record-as-traders-overlook-delayed-cuts-scenario</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 00:35:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
